# CODEOWNERS-SOFT - Notification-Only Code Ownership
#
# This file defines "soft" code ownership rules that notify teams but don't block PRs.
# Unlike the main CODEOWNERS file, these rules are for awareness and collaboration
# rather than mandatory approval.
#
# To implement soft ownership, you can:
# 1. Use automation tools that read this file and add reviewers as optional
# 2. Convert to regular CODEOWNERS during sensitive periods
# 3. Use in conjunction with draft PRs for early feedback
#
# File patterns follow the same syntax as CODEOWNERS

